        "pertanyaan": "<p>Monita : I visited four from six areas.<br>Andre : You said dedication area? What is that?<br>Monita : That is the area where important people planted<br>some trees there. Andre: I see. What about the<br>second area did you visit?<br>Monita : I visited the limited plants area.<br>Andre : What did you see there?<br>Monita : I saw some endangered trees in Kalimantan. I saw<br>pohon ulin there. People sometimes call it kayu besi.<\/p><p>Where did Monita see the pohon ulin?<\/p>",
