        "tema_cls": null,
        "no_kd": null,
        "pertanyaan": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Read the text again and answer the following questions.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Last semester, my school held an excursion to explore Labuan Bajo. It was a full day trip. Labuan Bajo is a hidden paradise situated in eastern Indonesia. We departed from school early in the morning so we could do many activities.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">What is the passage about?<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_a": "<p><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Labuan Bajo and its places.<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_b": "<p><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Exploring Labuan Bajo<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_c": "<p><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">The school excursion<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_d": "<p><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Indonesia as a country of treasures<\/span><\/p>",
