        "tema_cls": null,
        "no_kd": null,
        "pertanyaan": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(34,31,31);\">Read the text again and answer the following questions.<\/span><\/p><p>Exploring Labuan Bajo with all the activities made me realize that our country is \u201ca country of treasures\u201d. I felt so happy that I could enjoy all the activities that the package offered.<\/p><p>The writer probably feels \u2026 of Indonesia.<\/p>",
