        "pertanyaan": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(34,31,31);\">Read the text again and answer the following questions.<\/span><\/p><p>Before we &nbsp;went home, we went to Padar Island. <i>We wanted to see the landscape in panoramic view<\/i>, so we hiked for about 30 minutes to reach the peak. It was tiring, but the view was breathtaking. Padar Island is unique because it has several beaches with different colors.<\/p><p>The word \u201cit\u201d in \u201cPadar Island is unique because it has several \u2026\u201d refers to \u2026<\/p>",
