        "pertanyaan": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">Read the text again and answer the following questions.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The first place we visited was Wae Rana beach. It is a small beach, located between Binongko beach and Wae Cecu beach. We enjoyed the sunrise there. Too bad, people were not aware of the cleanliness. Litter was everywhere. The sunrise was beautiful, though. After enjoying the sunrise, we had breakfast. After we finished our breakfast, we went snorkeling. It was the first time for me to see sharks of all kinds. We could also see the underwater creatures, like bright coral, manta rays, turtles, seahorses, and fish.<\/p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#221F1F;\">The writer enjoyed the following while having shark diving, EXCEPT ....<\/span><\/p>",
